          "key": "C",
          "text": "RFC 1334"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "RFC 1661"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "RFC 1334",
      "explanation": "RFC 1334 introduced PPP, later expanded in RFC 1331 and RFC 1332. RFC 1661 is the current standard.",
      "difficulty": "medium"
    },
    {
